[Course_Description]
Are video production and post jobs futureproof? With artificial intelligence (AI) technology automating more and more tasks, what will the future of these professions look like? Will a line be drawn between creative and procedural tasks? In this course, Nick Harauz defines what AI is as it relates to video production and post. He looks at how AI is used in still photography and what it means for video and video production, including AI drones and trends in video editing and motion graphics software. He introduces findings from recent field studies as well as predictions about how the tools we've come to use and love will evolve. By the end of this course, you will understand the benefits and automation AI currently provides for your craft as well as how it will shape your future.